    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "0e937723-0662-4c93-b0a9-348769da0578",
    "sentence": "Growth in consumer spending has slowed and labor markets have softened.",
    "source": "statement_20080318.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2008-03-18",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "8415462e-87c9-4afb-96dc-430f5b38f038",
    "sentence": "The Committee also anticipates that inflation will settle, over coming quarters, at levels at or below those consistent with the Committeeâs dual mandate. However, the Committee will continue to pay close attention to the evolution of inflation and inflation expectations.",
    "source": "statement_20111213.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2011-12-13",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "4985a603-77d2-4761-8623-84170c0ab387",
    "sentence": "In support of its goals and in light of the shift in the balance of risks, the Committee decided to lower the target range for the federal funds rate by 1/4 percentage point to 3-1/2 to 3â3/4 percent.",
    "source": "statement_20251210.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2025-12-10",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "898c37f6-a49c-4c42-af68-f845d2d692da",
    "sentence": "Moreover, to help improve conditions in private credit markets, the Committee decided to purchase up to $300 billion of longer-term Treasury securities over the next six months.",
    "source": "statement_20090318.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2009-03-18",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "b07bc1c1-2e21-46ee-b0fb-1bc396be008f",
    "sentence": "In view of realized and expected labor market conditions and inflation, the Committee decided to raise the target range for the federal funds rate to 1-3/4 to 2 percent.",
    "source": "statement_20180613.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2018-06-13",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "7810c7d3-b264-4c19-aa7c-7ae44c8b0804",
    "sentence": "The Committee also will maintain its existing policy of reinvesting principal payments from its securities holdings.",
    "source": "statement_20110809.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2011-08-09",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "b3b28dc8-0ff1-4239-96d2-50c62ed08298",
    "sentence": "In addition, the Committee will continue reducing its holdings of Treasury securities and agency debt and agency mortgageâbacked securities.",
    "source": "statement_20240731.txt",
    "doc_type": "statement",
    "date": "2024-07-31",
    "context_question": null,
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
