  {
    "id": "be15b02f-b32b-4d23-b8ae-008e3d365337",
    "sentence": "To support a stronger economic recovery and to help ensure that inflation, over time, is at the rate most consistent with its dual mandate, the Committee agreed today to increase policy accommodation by purchasing additional agency mortgage-backed securities at a pace of $40 billion per month.",
