  {
    "id": "7924a06c-eb64-40b5-bdb8-6ca724a5cc67",
    "sentence": "In October, the Committee will initiate the balance sheet normalization program described in the June 2017 Addendum to the Committee's Policy Normalization Principles and Plans.",
